Uses of Class
org.jfree.chart.JFreeChart

Packages that use JFreeChart
Package
Description
org.jfree.chart
Core classes for JFreeChart including JFreeChart and ChartFactory.
org.jfree.chart.entity
Classes representing components of (or entities in) a chart.
org.jfree.chart.event
Event classes and listener interfaces, used to provide a change notification mechanism so that charts are automatically redrawn whenever changes are made to any chart component.
org.jfree.chart.plot
Plot classes and related interfaces.
org.jfree.chart.plot.pie
Classes used to create pie charts.
org.jfree.chart.swing
Classes that provide support for JFreeChart in Swing applications.
org.jfree.chart.swing.editor
Provides a simple (but so far incomplete) framework for editing chart properties.
